2305 Inner 2

In the SuperUser class, the getDescription method must take into account the country and city, i.e. return a result
similar to the following:
My name is George. I'm from the USA, Seattle.
Use the capabilities of the inner class.

Requirements:
1. The SuperUser class must be private.
2. The SuperUser class must contain the getDescription method.
3. The getDescription method in the SuperUser class must be public.
4. The getDescription method in the SuperUser class should return a string that takes into account the name, country
and city of the user formatted according to the condition of the task.
5. The getTrickyUser method should return an object of type SuperUser.